{"tid":2377942,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《驅魔麵館》完結在即　金世正透露感想：「這是讓我重新做夢的作品！」","createTime":"2021-01-24T05:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-24T05:42:37.000Z","uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1202a3dded11080c811929b720374e719f95406b","tid":2377942,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_b969bf3ed66655e088ced3d028dc9833/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-24/133234-894633.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_b969bf3ed66655e088ced3d028dc9833%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-24%2F133234-894633.png&h=55f226d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚《驅魔麵館》就會播出最後一集，這部戲不僅令許多觀眾印象深刻，對「都哈娜」金世正來說也別具意義！<br />\n<br />\n同時活躍在歌壇、影視圈，早已演出多部電視劇的金世正，近兩個月來憑著《驅魔麵館》備受喜愛，背後原因除了角色引發共鳴外，她的精湛詮釋也功不可沒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5ef6a834e7b3292c4783b1710fe7cdfe/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-24/133234-894635.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5ef6a834e7b3292c4783b1710fe7cdfe%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-24%2F133234-894635.jpg&h=d4ecbecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著《驅魔麵館》完結篇即將登場，今天（24 日）金世正透過經紀公司搶先分享了一路走來的心得：「其實我到現在都還沒真實地感覺到要完結了，可能是因為我相信不會就這樣結束吧！」<br />\n<br />\n「我因為《驅魔麵館》而重新有了夢想，開始變得能真心對待一切，也能用做自己、用自己的樣子開懷大笑。」金世正還透露自己在拍攝途中換了手機桌布：「我換成跟 Counter 的合照，上面還有這句話『要永遠努力，感謝自己獲得的一切，真心對待遇到的一切，不要畏縮、面對一切。』」<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_528f61fcab9ad756cf2f856269d854bb/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-01-24/133234-894634.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_528f61fcab9ad756cf2f856269d854bb%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-01-24%2F133234-894634.jpg&h=7fddb7f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金世正最後表示：「在我帶著更進步的面貌來跟大家見面前，希望我能加倍報答我獲得的幸福。謝謝所有得咁中和一起演戲的演員！」大家今晚一定要準時鎖定《驅魔麵館》完結篇！"},{"pid":"60e79403ab85d04c0838cda9e5b8cd7f15d595df","tid":2377942,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"天竺鼠車車好睇啲..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ffd1259377c8a04e798fe8eb4786c682aa2a71","tid":2377942,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60e79403ab85d04c0838cda9e5b8cd7f15d595df","tid":2377942,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"天竺鼠車車好睇啲..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"岩啊岩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c1806561cf72a0fb4e90b2b914831442693042f","tid":2377942,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:10:14.000Z","msg":"男人婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日返工先睇"},{"pid":"193e811a6cab52a41ce01b19d5ee738ca624a426","tid":2377942,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08ffd1259377c8a04e798fe8eb4786c682aa2a71","tid":2377942,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"60e79403ab85d04c0838cda9e5b8cd7f15d595df","tid":2377942,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:06:26.000Z","msg":"天竺鼠車車好睇啲..<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:08:39.000Z","msg":"岩啊岩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:10:30.000Z","msg":"@邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7849f7e52e27929bda541b4812f6a9f484bf6ce4","tid":2377942,"uid":25924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T05:11:00.000Z","msg":"正..<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c7ec9d696dea09631ee5b28e2940dfab7b119","tid":2377942,"uid":16659,"like":0,"di